/10/whitehaven-shooting-school-bus/1260655002/|title=MPD: Suspect in Whitehaven school bus shooting now in custody|website=The Commercial Appeal|accessdate=May 1, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|September 11, 2018\n|[[North Las Vegas, Nevada]]\n|1\n|0\n|18-year-old student Dalvin Brown was shot at [[Canyon Springs High School (North Las Vegas, Nevada)|Canyon Springs High School]] near the baseball field and later died of his injuries at a hospital.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rgj.com/story/news/crime/2018/09/12/police-north-las-vegas-school-shooting-victim-student/1281751002/|title=Police: North Las Vegas school shooting victim was student|website=Reno Gazette Journal|accessdate=May 1, 2019}}</ref> 16-year-old Kayin French was arrested in connection to Brown's death shortly after the incident. His trial is scheduled for February 3, 2020.<ref>https://www.ktnv.com/news/ccsd-approves-100k-settlement-to-mother-of-teen-shot-at-canyon-springs-hs</ref>\n|-\n|October 29, 2018\n|[[Matthews, North Carolina]]\n|1\n|1\n|A [[David W. Butler High School]] freshman, 16-year-old Jatwan Craig Cuffie, fatally shot sophomore Bobby McKeithen. Cuffie is in custody and charged with first-degree murder.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.charlotteobserver.com/news/local/article220780475.html|title=Bullying preceded fatal shooting of Butler High student, officials say|website=charlotteobserver|accessdate=May 1, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/10/29/cnn10/north-carolina-high-school-shooting/index.html|title=Student dies after shooting at North Carolina high school, police say|first=Jay|last=Croft|work=CNN|access-date=2018-10-29}}</ref> Cuffie was sentenced to 80 to 108 months in prison after pleading guilty to manslaughter.<ref>https://www.charlotteobserver.com/news/local/crime/article233106509.html</ref>\n|-\n|December 13, 2018\n|[[Richmond, Indiana]]\n|1<ref name=\":1\" group=\"n\" />\n|0\n|14-year-old Brandon Clegg<ref>{{cite web|url=https://chicago.cbslocal.com/2018/12/14/ri