ice investigate shooting inside classroom at Hamilton High |work = [[WMC-TV]] (Memphis, Tennessee) |date = February 4, 2008 |first = Kontji |last = Anthony |url-status=dead |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140302022256/http://www.wmctv.com/story/7818497/police-investigate-shooting-inside-classroom-at-hamilton-high |archivedate = March 2, 2014 |df = mdy-all |access-date = September 1, 2013 }}\n</ref>\n|-\n|{{dts|February 8, 2008}}\n|{{sort|Baton Rouge, Louisiana}}\n|3<ref name=\":1\" group=\"n\" />\n|0\n|Latina Williams, a 23-year-old nursing student at [[Louisiana Technical College]] killed two classmates and herself in a second floor classroom.<ref>\n{{cite news |url = http://www.wafb.com/Global/story.asp?S=7842633 |title = 3 Dead in LTC Shooting |work = [[WAFB]] (Baton Rouge, Louisiana) |date = February 8, 2008 |url-status=dead |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131224095333/http://www.wafb.com/Global/story.asp?S=7842633 |archivedate = December 24, 2013 |df = mdy-all |access-date = December 23, 2013 }}\n</ref>\n|-\n|{{dts|February 11, 2008}}\n|{{sort|Miami Gardens, Florida}}\n|0\n|1\n|43-year-old 11th grade algebra teacher, Sergio Miranda, was shot by 19-year-old Patrick Lively, outside [[Miami Carol City Senior High School]] during a robbery but was expected to survive.<ref>{{cite news |url = https://www.cbsnews.com/news/florida-teacher-shot-during-smoke-break/ |title = Florida Teacher Shot During Smoke Break |work = [[CBS News]] |date = November 6, 2007 |url-status=live |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160422083013/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/florida-teacher-shot-during-smoke-break/ |archivedate = April 22, 2016 |df = mdy-all }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.wibw.com/home/headlines/11058911.html |title = Teacher Shot At South Florida High School |work = [[WIBW-TV]] (Topeka, Kansas) |date = November 6, 2007 |url-status=live |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160419002504/http://www.wibw.com/home/headlines/11058911