ol-shooting/index.html School shooting reported in Santa Clarita] CNN, November 14, 2019</ref>\n|-\n|November 15, 2019\n|[[Pleasantville, New Jersey]]\n|1\n|2\n|Five men opened fire during a playoff game between the Camden Panthers and the Pleasantville Greyhounds at [[Pleasantville High School (New Jersey)|Pleasantville High School]], injuring a 15-year-old boy, a 27-year-old male, and fatally injuring a 10-year-old boy. All five were later arrested for the random act of violence however the injured 27 year-old (who is believed to be the shooters target) has also been charged with unlawful possession of a handgun.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/ny-five-charged-new-jersey-high-school-football-game-shooting-20191116-fvj6h4fx5rginkdfc3ueggwlxu-story.html|title=5 men charged over \u2018petty vengeance\u2019 shooting that caused mass panic at packed N.J. high school football game|last=Dillon|first=Nancy|website=nydailynews.com|access-date=2019-11-17}}</ref><ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/</ref><ref>https://6abc.com/men-charged-in-high-school-football-game-shooting-to-appear-in-court/5710940/</ref><ref name=\"goodmorningamerica.com\"/> The alleged shooter Alvin Wyatt has been charged with murder and attempted murder.<ref>https://abcnews.go.com/US/schools-shootings-common-incidents-radar-2019/story?id=67040402</ref>\n|-\n|November 23, 2019\n|[[Union City, California]]\n|2\n|0\n|Two boys, aged 11 and 14-years-old were shot in the parking lot of the Seamless Elementary School around 1 am, while sitting in a minivan. Both boys died of their wounds, one at the scene and the other at the hospital.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/11/24/us/california-elementary-school-shooting/index.html|title=2 boys shot dead while sitting in a van at an elementary school parking lot|last=Karimi|first=Faith|last2=Kallingal|first2=Mallika|date=November 24, 2019|website=CNN|access-date=2019-11-26}}</ref> 18-year-old year Jason Cornejo of Castro Valley